SUMMARY:
This program implements the model of:
A. Litwin-Kumar, R. Rosenbaum, & B. Doiron. Inhibitory stabilization and visual coding in cortical circuits with multiple interneuron subtypes. Journal of Neurophysiology (2016).

REQUIREMENTS:
This program requires Julia (julialang.org). Tested on Julia 1.0.

USE:
To run the simulation, enter the command include("runsim.jl") from a Julia interactive session.  

